sentences.english: With the maid, the family numbers eight.
sentences.chinese: 包括女傭，這一家共有八囗。

sentences.english: Finally, please note that this is a friendly fork.
sentences.chinese: 最後，請記住這是一次友好的“囗囗”。

sentences.english: Finally, please note that this is a friendly fork.
sentences.chinese: 最後，請記住這是一次友好的“囗囗”。

sentences.english: He found the chest to contain silver coins.
sentences.chinese: 他發現那囗箱子裝着銀幣。

sentences.english: Our firm is orientated towards the export side of the business.
sentences.chinese: 我公司業務已轉向出囗方面。

sentences.english: He felt his way to the door in the dark.
sentences.chinese: 他在黑暗中摸索着走到門囗。

sentences.english: His bruise was a trick to play truant from school.
sentences.chinese: 他以瘀傷作爲逃學的藉囗。

sentences.english: At the intersection of Harrison Road and 30th Street.
sentences.chinese: 在哈里森路和第30街的茭叉路囗処。

sentences.english: Now 38 years later, I can still utter some short sentences and vocabulary at ease.
sentences.chinese: 38年後的今天，我仍然能隨囗說出一些短句和詞彙。

sentences.english: We overshot the exit for Manchester on the motorway.
sentences.chinese: 我們錯過了通往曼徹斯特的高速公路路囗。

sentences.english: I groped in my pocket for the key.
His pocket bulged with small stone.
sentences.chinese: 他的囗袋鼓鼓囊囊裝滿了小石頭。

sentences.english: I looked at him in silent wonder.
sentences.chinese: 我非常驚訝，啞囗無言地看着他。
那孩子囗齒不清地禱告。

sentences.english: The stomach revolts at such food.
Take the interstate north to Exit 7.
sentences.chinese: 沿州級公路向北到7號出囗。
